# Deployment Steps

## For Android
* Set-up a publisher topic called "wishing-well"
* Create a service account key with Publisher and Subscriber permissions 
* Export the service account key and replace the one in app/assets/key.json 
* Test the app end to end 
* Rebuild the app and update the distfiles 

## For Cloud function
* Set-up a cloud function to publish the flag to the topic 
* Set-up a cloud scheduler set to "* * * * *" using default compute engine account to trigger the cloud function
